Galil stepper closed loop tuning experince

1) KS is a very important factor during tuning process

When motor speed is high, try to lower the KS value. use KS=16 as a standard. Then increase or decrease.

2) IT is a very important factor as well. use IT as 0.1 as a standard. the minumum is 0.04

3) K1 is a very important factor

4) K2 KP KI are less important.

First set K1 to a value like 5. and rest K2,Kp,KI to 0.
